{"tid":2004741,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"點解話唔支援Smart Octopus嘅電話係垃圾呢？因為只有良心嘅廠商先俾到香港人「Felica」NFC-F！","createTime":"2020-05-06T15:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T05:41:15.000Z","uid":109923,"like":16,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d0404f51736ac34b8d80063aa5df8920ede7b015","tid":2004741,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:41:42.000Z","msg":"八達通「嘟」機付款需要用到「Felica (NFC type-F)」<br />\n<br />\n　　八達通對應Apple Pay的功能，上年宣佈會在2019年內推出，不過在上年底已宣佈延期至2020年。至於為甚麼只有少數Android手機用到智能八達通，不是大部份Android機一早已經有NFC功能可以查詢八達通卡餘額嗎？<br />\n<br />\n　　因為NFC技術是一個統稱，實際上有分 Type - A、B、F、V。八達通和日本大部份的非接觸式支付裝置，用的都是「Felica (NFC type-F)」標準，IC卡或手機裝置要配備FeliCa晶片才能做到「嘟卡」、「嘟機」付款。<br />\n<br />\n　　八達通技術總監甘志深（Sammy）指出，NFC是一個國際標準，手機有NFC功能加上廠方有開放使用，就能和八達通卡溝通讀寫，但去到付款的步驟還是要用回「Felica (NFC type-F)」的技術。因此就算不對應Smart Octopus的Android手機或是現階段未對應Apple Pay的iPhone，用八達通app可查看餘額，亦可用O! ePay增值，只是如沒有FeliCa晶片，就不能像Samsung Pay的智能八達卡般，直接用手機變做八達通「嘟」機付款了。<br />\n<br />\n　　例如Samsung手機都要有安裝FeliCa晶片才支援，多數是中至高檔機才做到。Apple日後開放智能八達通功能都是iPhone 7日本版以上的型號才能對應，6s是不行的。」目前iPhone 8之後的型號都配備FeliCa晶片。<br />\n<br />\n支援NFC Type-F嘅iPhone：<br />\niPhone 7 (只限日版)<br />\niPhone 8﹑8 Plus、X打後、Apple Watch Series 3打後全部支援<br />\n<br />\n支援NFC Type-F嘅Samsung機：<br />\nGalaxy Z Flip、Fold、Note10+、Note10、Note10 Lite、Note9、Note8、S20 Ultra、S20+、S20、S10、S10+、S10e、S9、S9+、S8、S8+、A80、A71、A70、A60、A51、A50s、A9、A8s、A8 Star、A8+、C9 Pro、C7 Pro、C5 Pro<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日版Pixel 3代就開始有Felica，日本以外嘅版本一律cut cost無Felica！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YnK8vX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYnK8vX4.jpg&h=c8f4a47a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSony 舊年旗艦機Xperia 1香港版一樣冇FeliCa<br />\n<strong>呢啲次級硬件嘅電話=垃圾=唔支援Smart Octopus</strong>"},{"pid":"40f4fc444a69c81064d45dd5fded29270e2207a6","tid":2004741,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXhFnbM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXhFnbM.gif&h=aa2c69d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c08a1b1d4f1e8829c9f775d18f875709a0725a6","tid":2004741,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"好耐之前<br />\n我用Asus Zenfone2 + 八達通SIM<br />\n係嘟到<br />\n<br />\n熄咗機/上唔到網嘟唔到咁解"},{"pid":"3dd929595e213baf6ae7c3d6a5e3f3c2cafc8250","tid":2004741,"uid":47042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"可見將來都無消息 Google Pay Google Pay 會支援 Smart Octopus<br />\n但三星以外既 Android 機好多都可以用八仔sim<br />\n八仔Sim 唔洗 Felica chip"},{"pid":"e7a2aa08624d2b743f4b276b3464e409e2d8eb52","tid":2004741,"uid":48064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c08a1b1d4f1e8829c9f775d18f875709a0725a6","tid":2004741,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"好耐之前<br />\n我用Asus Zenfone2 + 八達通SIM<br />\n係嘟到<br />\n<br />\n熄咗機/上唔到網嘟唔到咁解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"我好耐之前用xperia V 同 G2 都嘟到 不過要磨勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個時試過搭巴士見有個西裝友磨到下個站先嘟到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b6d13a41d89f3f0a445f1afc2a72cb4d43f5d2","tid":2004741,"uid":220345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dd929595e213baf6ae7c3d6a5e3f3c2cafc8250","tid":2004741,"uid":47042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"可見將來都無消息 Google Pay Google Pay 會支援 Smart Octopus<br />\n但三星以外既 Android 機好多都可以用八仔sim<br />\n八仔Sim 唔洗 Felica chip"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:14:02.000Z","msg":"用到但八仔sim=限咗你用咩台呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525f3cfcbdd4435dd02897e9047d2a3c322af7cc","tid":2004741,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b6d13a41d89f3f0a445f1afc2a72cb4d43f5d2","tid":2004741,"uid":220345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dd929595e213baf6