"pid":"dd6c9b938be4b185cfe365827cb349f89a3a7c43","tid":2004741,"uid":253343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c08a1b1d4f1e8829c9f775d18f875709a0725a6","tid":2004741,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T15:46:33.000Z","msg":"好耐之前<br />\n我用Asus Zenfone2 + 八達通SIM<br />\n係嘟到<br />\n<br />\n熄咗機/上唔到網嘟唔到咁解"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T13:39:46.000Z","msg":"octopus sim 係因為張sim 有 nfc-f <br />\n但同時要同機內nfc a/b 比電張sim 卡 先用到的<br />\n<br />\n如果部機本身無nfc a/b 都係用唔到 octopus sim 的<br />\n<br />\n依家唔會有sim 卡內置octopus"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T18:07:43.000Z","msg":"點解我Pixel 2 xl用唔到octopus sim <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇nfc a/b?<br />\n咁普遍nfc chip係咩type?"},{"pid":"2314cf5ff0c3968d39edb4d2c1359252d335cb96","tid":2004741,"uid":61954,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aba71a3ba56faea4a9f87f643bc47c7daae81269","tid":2004741,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d344ffa0a56dc086d2f8e508bfeb826210708e27","tid":2004741,"uid":23162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"咁八達通Sim咩原理？部機都係冇Felica chip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T17:58:58.000Z","msg":"sim只係個id<br />\n<br />\n都係要有FeliCa先得<br />\n<br />\npixel 3就係例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T18:43:29.000Z","msg":"唔識就咪鳩吹啦<br />\n八達通sim自帶FeliCa晶片㗎"},{"pid":"8652aa9dbcbeee816f21858519f73b91ce831fe8","tid":2004741,"uid":64918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T20:13:24.000Z","msg":"如果我冇記錯, NFC-F 同埋 Felica 都仲有少少分別. Felica 嗰個 Security Key 唔係 Open Standard. 亦都即係話你要同而家 Felica 裝置 Connect, 你仍然都係需要俾錢買一條 Key ( 冇記錯係 Sony ). <br />\n<br />\n我有啲印象當初係有傾過將呢個 Key Standard / Key Issuing Organisation 分拆出嚟. 但係都已經差唔多係兩年嘅前嘅事. 而家係點就唔知."},{"pid":"9c2dd0164549a7d834b03ed34d8f2a443bb465c5","tid":2004741,"uid":229459,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T23:16:38.000Z","msg":"香港八仔落到Apple pay 你真係要多謝日本人，如果唔係佢地market 大，同apple傾掂數，FeliCa 無乜機會內置iPhone"},{"pid":"e02461311dc6d7a1e2b7783b07852e224a2ae9a4","tid":2004741,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"三叔開放日本felica先講啦，得日本版用得。iphone都唔會分日本版香港版限定交通卡啦"},{"pid":"e2aadfc6090a4eaa84f5dd8b037a435bf7f62a45","tid":2004741,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e02461311dc6d7a1e2b7783b07852e224a2ae9a4","tid":2004741,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"三叔開放日本felica先講啦，得日本版用得。iphone都唔會分日本版香港版限定交通卡啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:54:36.000Z","msg":"iPhone 7有分日版<br />\n<br />\n就係有FeliCa"},{"pid":"6cf68dc27bc84dcadc25e027db2917c4939fc6cb","tid":2004741,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2aadfc6090a4eaa84f5dd8b037a435bf7f62a45","tid":2004741,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e02461311dc6d7a1e2b7783b07852e224a2ae9a4","tid":2004741,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"三叔開放日本felica先講啦，得日本版用得。iphone都唔會分日本版香港版限定交通卡啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:54:36.000Z","msg":"iPhone 7有分日版<br />\n<br />\n就係有FeliCa"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:55:33.000Z","msg":"之後嗰啲無啦，三叔新機係咪無分？"},{"pid":"a420ae62ddb1f4a099ebdc95748448b2e3d0c898","tid":2004741,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cf68dc27bc84dcadc25e027db2917c4939fc6cb","tid":2004741,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2aadfc6090a4eaa84f5dd8b037a435bf7f62a45","tid":2004741,"uid":229459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e02461311dc6d7a1e2b7783b07852e224a2ae9a4","tid":2004741,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:53:36.000Z","msg":"三叔開放日本felica先講啦，得日本版用得。iphone都唔會分日本版香港版限定交通卡啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T00:54:36.000Z","msg":"iP